data.description: Stop the car!!!! This property has everything you could possibly want to feel at home and never leave.  This home features 4 bedrooms and 3 full baths with every luxury you could hope for.   3 beautiful acres with plenty of space for any type of fur baby you have. Recent remodel inside the home with Luxury custom cabinets, high tier granite, top tier fixtures, Viking appliances and beautiful tile.  The backyard is nothing short of an outdoor resort with a beautiful pool/spa combo, and large covered patio.  If those weren't enough, a 2200 kw whole house generator, slab with Rv connections, and Anderson Low E windows throughout the house.  Combine that with being located in beautiful Magnolia this is a can't miss! Motivated seller!! Bring us an offer
